# Aggressive deny-list: only `dist/` and `devops/` are needed by the Dockerfile.
# Everything else (deploy/, src/, node_modules/, cdk.out/, …) is excluded both
# to keep build context small and to prevent CDK DockerImageAsset hashing from
# recursing into deploy/cdk.out/ asset folders.
*
!dist
!devops
!.dockerignore
